name: The "Ship of Space" - Galactibles™ #14
description: Holy Tractor Beams! You’ve discovered Galactible™ #14,  the “Ship of Space!” Collect this stellar spaceship to traverse the star clustered galaxies of the Galactiverse! Comes with a wicked stereo system, photon laser cannons, one high-powered death ray, and a slappin' groove for you to Pew Pew Pew to! Your Mana has been raised by +15,000,000 bits! Custom beat made by Pyramid Guy! Galactibles™ are one-of-a-kind and minted as 1-of-1. Only 99 will be made! New Galactibles™ drop every week (sorta) on twitter, so give us a follow @Galactibles! Certified authentic and original animations made by Pyramid Guy (IG: @pyramidguy), aka Kris Kanaly (TW: @kriskanaly). Galactibles™ ©2021 | galactibles.com
